front.title: Intruder Missile
front.gametext: Deploy on your B-wing, Z-95, YT-1300 Transport, or Falcon. May target a capital starship for free. Draw destiny. Add 3 if that capital starship was targeted by another weapon this turn. Target hit if total destiny > defense value. After firing, place Missile in Used Pile.
front.lore: Prototype missile developed by Slayn & Korpil. Ionizing warhead disrupts onboard systems. Capable of destroying capital starships by overloading shield generators.

pulledBy: Lieutenant s'Too Vees (when at a docking bay)
